 will 100% take place. Please accept this notification as either assurance or warning.”</p><p> The musician is no stranger to cancelling shows. His recently announced 2025 UK dates Morrissey&#39;s first in the country since <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-summer-2023-uk-ireland-tour-tickets-3425160">abruptly cancelling a show at London&#39;s Crystal Palace back in April 2023</a> . The gig was set for July 9, and around that same time, the singer announced a tour of the UK and Ireland, including a replacement date for July 9. </p><figure id="attachment_3841183" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841183" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841183" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-performing-3.jpg" alt="Morrissey performs onstage during day 2 of the Firefly Music Festival on June 19, 2015 in Dover, Delaware. (Photo by Ilya S. Savenok/Getty Images for Firefly)" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-performing-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-performing-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-performing-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-performing-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-performing-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-performing-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841183" class="wp-caption-text"> Morrissey performs onstage during day 2 of the Firefly Music Festival on June 19, 2015 in Dover, Delaware. (Photo by Ilya S. Savenok/Getty Images for Firefly)</figcaption></figure><p> His July 9 show  – <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-cancels-sold-out-nottingham-show-3467003">which was set to take place at Nottingham&#39;s Royal Concert Hall</a> – was then cancelled, with the venues hosting the shows citing “unforeseen circumstances”.</p><p> All new shows are taking place following <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-announces-december-2024-shows-including-new-years-eve-gig-in-la-3819363">a brief run of Los Angeles gigs to round off 2024</a> , as well as <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-announces-2024-north-american-tour-kicking-off-on-halloween-3781107">a sold-out tour of North America in late October and November</a> .</p><p> The live shows follow the new updates the singer has given over new material in recent months – namely the long-delayed album &#39;Bonfire Of The Teenagers&#39;.</p><p> The singer went on to share a statement on <a href="https://www.morrisseycentral.com/messagesfrommorrissey/387636-bonfire-of-teenagers-is-none-of-your-business">his website</a> around the status of &#39;Bonfire&#39;, accusing Capitol Records of “fascism” and having a “creeping culture of censorship”. He also said that he was <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-is-quickly-coming-around-to-that-belief-that-capitol-is-sabotaging-his-new-album-3394087">“quickly coming around to” the belief that the brand only signed &#39;Bonfire Of Teenagers&#39; “in order to sabotage it”</a> . </p><figure id="attachment_3841184" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841184" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841184" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-posing.jpg" alt="Morrissey performs live on stage at 02 Arena on November 29, 2014 in London, England. (Photo by Jim Dyson/WireImage)" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Morrissey-posing-800x508.jpg